ase for Documents and FAQs, Bookings and Appointments For WooCommerce Premium, WP Media Folders, Chamber Dashboard Business Directory, Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4797:\"<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/echo-knowledge-base/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Knowledge Base for Documents and FAQs</a>, <a href=\"https://www.pluginhive.com/product/woocommerce-booking-and-appointments/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bookings and Appointments For WooCommerce Premium</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-media-folders/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">WP Media Folders</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chamber-dashboard-business-directory/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Chamber Dashboard Business Directory</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/massive-addons-for-visual-composer/14429839\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Knowledge Base for Documents and FAQs</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This is a WordPress Knowledge Base plugin for articles, documents and FAQs.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/echo-knowledge-base/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download Knowledge Base for Documents and FAQs</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Bookings and Appointments For WooCommerce Premium</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Woocommerce Bookings and appointments is a plugin that allows you to convert your time, products or services into a bookable resource.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.pluginhive.com/product/woocommerce-booking-and-appointments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Purchase Bookings and Appointments For WooCommerce Premium</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WP Media Folders</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Plugin changes the attachments actual folder on the server.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-media-folders/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download WP Media Folders</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Chamber Dashboard Business Directory</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Creates a business directory on WordPress site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chamber-dashboard-business-directory/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download Chamber Dashboard Business Directory</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/massive-addons-for-visual-composer/14429839\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Purchase Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EyGqACribVM:B2m-T6PPJAU:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/EyGqACribVM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wpml.org/2019/03/compatible-wpml-plugins-march-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_bas